name: TributeToJim
description: A Tribute to Jim Morrison who died 50 years ago in Paris, France. He was a true American poet and became famous in just a short period of time. As I grew up listening to my Dads LPs, theDoors came to me to stay. He influenced me in terms of music and art. The last buyer of the NFT will get a physical high res/quality Print (Please contact me via Twitter DM). 100x100cm equivalent 40“x40“.
